name: Motive Research Fleet Management
overview:
Motive Research is a leading provider of fleet management solutions and GPS vehicle tracking services in Melbourne. Our solutions bring increased mobile workforce productivity and get down fleet operating cost.

At Motive Research our expertise and experience in the industry has enabled us to offer complete range of GPS tracking solution & fleet management systems and thus we serve best suitable solutions for the lowest investment.

Services we offer: • GPS Fleet Management • GPS Asset Tracking • Job Dispatch & Navigation • Trailer & Container Tracking • Taxi Dispatch Solution • GPS Mining Solutions • Personal GPS Tracking • Plant & Equipment Tracking • Local Government Solutions
